<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[<span class="c2">(٢٠٧٢)</span> -<span class="c5"> (حديث:</span> <span class="c1">" عفى لأمتى عن الخطأ والنسيان "</span>.]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
